{"tid":1850422,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"感覺而家有股風向導人做埋啲騎呢、害人害己嘅嘢嚟「防疫」","createTime":"2020-01-29T13:46:36.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-30T16:53:52.000Z","uid":208722,"like":32,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"0afbcc12188688f4a5358547c0b677b2677c2432","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:46:36.000Z","msg":"大家笑鳩元秋蒸口罩，但其實連登都有類似post。或者可能我小人之心去度真心，但突然咁大量嘅post，我多少都有懷疑：<br />\n<br />\n[認真一問] 經紫外光燈照過 口罩可否重用?<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850337\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850337</a><br />\n<br />\n拎紫外光燈消毒個口罩可唔可以重用？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850303\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850303</a><br />\n<br />\n微波爐叮口罩重用得唔得？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849645\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849645</a><br />\n<br />\n低風險人士用自己的烤箱自行消毒口罩重用，可行嗎？<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850300\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850300</a><br />\n<br />\n使唔使咁誇張，香港又冇爆發，人人搶口罩，個個戴<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850187\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850187</a><br />\n<br />\n陳雲：我唔帶口罩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850332\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850332</a><br />\n<br />\n而咁啱過去半日，支共中央電視叫人唔好換口罩，甚至唔使某啲場合戴口罩<br />\n<br />\n中央嗌人唔好換口罩<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1849957\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1849957</a><br />\n<br />\n元秋同廣州博士之後就即刻教人蒸口罩，再加埋上面啲post，聽第一二次就可能好笑，但一多呢類Post，就會有人開始相信，再加上危機逼近，逐漸就會變成群眾嘅認知倒錯，令集體防疫失效。<br />\n<br />\n如果屬實，真心覺得支共「大外宣」好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3260124e9b8c3e651f9c275000c4e11c9e531f91","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:48:45.000Z","msg":"乾焗口罩重用<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1850423\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1850423</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n又一個"},{"pid":"d7ff69eecfde28b1673e500d4ab872d31740ade7","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:50:11.000Z","msg":"似是而非嘅潛移默化，係最容易推人落深淵，武漢有辦你睇"},{"pid":"fd0b20b3f50667e0a8cd7eca54a3cf8262a6283b","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:53:12.000Z","msg":"一個人同你講咩蒸口罩焗口罩重用，你可能一笑置之；但當十個、百個重覆嘅訊息出現嗰陣，人會對資訊疲勞，怠於分辨資訊真偽，呢個先最危險"},{"pid":"0f924eac05d43b5ca3d908792330c2d6d55dd204","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:55:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a24c8895403d1bc8695c5de3c03f7359c0e2aea5","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:56:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c66b1f58a8f3cfe5d37f5779c74523442da5479","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:58:28.000Z","msg":"支共不嬲想香港人死，聽佢講咩蒸焗重用，盞死多兩錢重<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11290bfc66c4bb926881ebae8a63cb8bbc983847","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T13:59:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"210e4e9a3b058b58799f644906959f749a4fde0f","tid":1850422,"uid":208722,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:02:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a1b4d7618ea7799e1dfe03de3b74ae6aebf0f2b","tid":1850422,"uid":161374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-29T14:16:04.000Z","msg":"唔好重用口罩，無就唔好出街"},{"pid":"fceae